cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Triadic Reality Theory: Finite Logic, Infinite Information, and Actualizing Action as the Foundation of Physical Reality"
message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Longmire
    given-names: James D.
