version: "0.9"
date-released: "2026-06"
url: "https://github.com/jdlongmire/triadic-reality-theory"
abstract: >
  Triadic Reality Theory proposes that actualized physical reality is constituted
  by three co-requiring primitives: finite logical constraint, infinite
  informational potential, and actualizing action. It is offered as a candidate
  foundational ontology and research program, not a completed physical theory.
